posting_body: ['PROPERTY INFO', 'ID: 11791995', 'Rent: $1,600 / Month', 'Beds: 1', 'Bath: 1', 'Available Date: 08/01/2022', 'Pet: Cats Only', 'Rent Includes:: Electricity, Gas, Heat, Hot Water', 'Parking:: off-street parking', 'PLEASE CALL 781-962-6615 WITH QUESTIONS OR TO SCHEDULE A VIEWING.', ' VIEWINGS CAN NOT BE SCHEDULED VIA EMAIL OR TEXT.', 'Garden Level 1 bedroom unit features a spacious eat-in, fully applianced kitchen with dishwasher, disposal, gas range, and refrigerator.', 'There is a spacious living room with a working fireplace, a full tiled bath, and 1 bedroom.', 'There is an overabundance of closet spaces as well as access to a coin-operated washer and dryer.', 'This unit has its own private entrance.', 'Heat and electricity are included in the monthly rent.', 'Off-street parking for 1 car only.', 'This property is located in Arlington Heights near the Lexington line and there is easy access to public transportation and rt 2/128/90.', "Close to Trader Joe's and all that Arlington Heights has to offer.", 'Sorry, no pets, and smoking is not permitted inside the unit.', 'Available 8/01/22.', 'FIRST, SECURITY.', 'Agency Fee', '**APPLICANTS MUST HAVE GOOD CREDIT', 'FEATURES', 'Ceramic Tiled Bath', 'Coin-op laundry on site', 'Dishwasher', 'Disposal', 'Eat-in Kitchen', 'Fireplace', 'Living Room', 'Separate Kitchen', 'Prices and availability are subject to change without notice.', ' Photos of managed buildings may be representative only and not of the actual unit available.', ' Not responsible for typographical errors.']
